Architectural lineage:
  - GospelMap (2024–2025) — prototype: church finder, justice network, accountability
  - Catholic Network Tools (2025) — full platform identity
  - Jumuia (2025–present) — production release: parish coordination + USSD + M-Pesa

Named after the AMECEA tradition of Small Christian Communities (SCCs / Jumuia):
  the church as a network of local, accountable communities.

